@startuml BoraxTheClean_DevelopmentMachine
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "GitHub" {
  rectangle "GitHub Actions\nWorkflow" as GHWorkflow
  rectangle "Repository" as Repo
}

rectangle "AWS" {
  rectangle "CloudFormation" as CF
  rectangle "EC2 Instance" as EC2
  rectangle "IAM Role" as IAM
  rectangle "Security Group" as SG
  rectangle "CloudWatch Alarm" as CWAlarm
}

Dev --> Repo : Push changes
Repo --> GHWorkflow : Trigger workflow
GHWorkflow --> CF : Deploy stack
CF --> EC2 : Create instance
CF --> IAM : Attach role
CF --> SG : Configure access
CF --> CWAlarm : Setup inactivity monitor

EC2 --> IAM : Assume role
EC2 --> SG : Enforce network rules
CWAlarm --> EC2 : Stop if inactive

note right of SG
  Security Concern:
  Allows SSH from all IPs
end note

note right of IAM
  Security Concern:
  Uses AdministratorAccess
end note
@enduml